3.3, 1093.8, 774.1]}, {"text": "partnerships have an interest. Accordingly, the Company receives producing well overhead, drilling well overhead", "bbox": [143.8, 778.3, 1094.1, 799.2]}, {"text": "and other fees related to the operation of the properties. The affiliated partnerships also reimburse the Company for", "bbox": [143.8, 803.4, 1094.2, 824.2]}, {"text": "their allocated share of general and administrative charges. Reimbursements of fees are recorded as reductions to", "bbox": [143.8, 828.3, 1094.1, 849.1]}, {"text": "general and administrative expenses in the Company’s Consolidated Statements of Operations.", "bbox": [143.8, 853.4, 949.7, 874.2]}, {"text": "The activities with affiliated partnerships are summarized for the following related party transactions for the", "bbox": [185.5, 896.0, 1094.2, 916.8]}, {"text": "years ended December 31, 2005, 2004 and 2003:", "bbox": [143.8, 921.1, 562.8, 941.9]}, {"text": "2005", "bbox": [830.1, 981.4, 863.4, 998.0]}, {"text": "2004", "bbox": [918.7, 981.4, 952.0, 998.0]}, {"text": "2003", "bbox": [1007.2, 981.4, 1040.5, 998.0]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [840.8, 958.5, 1029.8, 975.1]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [883.3, 1004.3, 987.7, 1021.0]}, {"text": "Receipt of lease operating and supervision charges in accordance with", "bbox": [185.5, 1030.5, 785.0, 1051.3]}, {"text": "standard industry operating agreements . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [206.4, 1053.4, 797.2, 1074.2]}, {"text": "$1,493", "bbox": [818.0, 1053.4, 875.3, 1074.2]}, {"text": "$1,458", "bbox": [906.6, 1053.4, 963.9, 1074.2]}, {"text": "$1,473", "bbox": [995.2, 1053.4, 1052.6, 1074.2]}, {"text": "Reimbursement of general and administrative expenses . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 1082.6, 797.2, 1103.4]}, {"text": "$ 348", "bbox": [818.0, 1082.6, 875.4, 1103.4]}, {"text": "$ 193", "bbox": [906.6, 1082.6, 964.0, 1103.4]}, {"text": "$ 148", "bbox": [995.2, 1082.6, 1052.5, 1103.4]}, {"text": "NOTE H.", "bbox": [143.8, 1142.6, 230.3, 1163.5]}, {"text": "Incentive Plans", "bbox": [251.2, 1142.6, 388.8, 1163.5]}, {"text": "Retirement Plans", "bbox": [164.7, 1185.3, 315.3, 1206.1]}, {"text": "Deferred compensation retirement plan.", "bbox": [185.5, 1228.0, 535.2, 1248.9]}, {"text": "In August 1997, the Compensation Committee of the Board of", "bbox": [556.1, 1228.2, 1094.2, 1249.1]}, {"text": "Directors (the “Board”) approved a deferred compensation retirement plan for the officers and certain key", "bbox": [143.8, 1253.2, 1094.2, 1274.0]}, {"text": "employees of the Company. Each officer and key employee is allowed to contribute up to 25 percent of their", "bbox": [143.8, 1278.2, 1093.9, 1299.1]}, {"text": "base salary and 100 percent of their annual bonus. The Company will provide a matching contribution of 100 percent", "bbox": [143.8, 1303.3, 1093.9, 1324.1]}, {"text": "of the officer’s and key employee’s contribution limited to the first 10 percent of the officer’s base salary and eight", "bbox": [143.8, 1328.2, 1094.0, 1349.0]}, {"text": "percent of the key employee’s base salary. The Company’s matching contribution vests immediately. A trust fund", "bbox": [143.8, 1353.2, 1094.1, 1374.1]}, {"text": "has been established by the Company to accumulate the contributions made under this retirement plan. The", "bbox": [143.8, 1378.3, 1094.0, 1399.1]}, {"text": "Company’s matching contributions were $1.2 million, $.9 million and $.9 million for the years ended December 31,", "bbox": [143.8, 1403.2, 1094.2, 1424.1]}, {"text": "2005, 2004 and 2003, respectively.", "bbox": [143.8, 1428.3, 440.6, 1449.1]}, {"text": "87", "bbox": [608.6, 1478.2, 629.5, 1499.1]}, {"text": "PIONEER NATURAL RESOURCES COMPANY", "bbox": [394.2, 116.4, 844.1, 137.2]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS", "bbox": [344.7, 154.0, 893.5, 174.8]}, {"text": "December 31, 2005, 2004 and 2003", "bbox": [462.2, 179.0, 775.9, 199.8]}]}